+++ ðŸŒˆPride Header
If you would like to use only the animated rainbow header, insert this line of code:
> [[include :scp-wiki:component:pride-logos ###e70|header=##-]]]
This could coexist with the logo. For example, if you want to use both the logo and the header:
> [[include :scp-wiki:component:pride-logos s10=-]| ###e70|header=##-]| ###0a0|code=##phil| ##blue|code2=##intersex]]
Please notice that using this header will necessarily introduce the default Sigma header background to your page. This might overwrite other customized header backgrounds.
